quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  51,47,Aasman ko humne apne zoar se banaya hai aur hum iski qudrat rakhte hain
  51,48,Zameen ko humne bichaya hai aur hum badey acchey hamwar(Smoothers/ spread) karne waley hain
  51,49,"Aur har cheez ke humne jodey banaye hain, shayad ke tum ussey sabaq lo"
  51,50,"To daudo Allah ki taraf , main tumahre liye us ki taraf se saaf saaf khabardar karne wala hoon"
  51,51,Aur na banao Allah ke saath koi dusra mabood. Main tumahre liye uski taraf se saaf saaf khabardar karne wala hoon
  51,52,"Yunhi hota raha hai, inse pehle ki qaumon ke paas bhi koi Rasool aisa nahin aaya jisey unhon ne yeh na kaha ho ke yeh saahir (sorcerer) hai ya majnoon(deewana)"
  51,53,"Kya in sab ne apas mein ispar koi samjhauta karliya hai? Nahin, balke yeh sab sarkash log hain"
  51,54,"Pas aey Nabi, inse rukh pher lo, tumpar kuch malamat nahin"
  51,55,"Albatta nasihat karte raho, kyunke nasihat imaan laney walon ke liye nafeh(faiyda-mand) hai"
  51,56,Maine Jinn aur Insano ko iske siwa kisi kaam ke liye paida nahin kiya hai ke woh meri bandagi karein
  51,57,Main unsey koi rizq nahin chahta aur na yeh chahta hoon ke woh mujhey khilayein
  51,58,"Allah to khud hi Razzak hai, badi quwwat wala aur zabardast"
  51,59,"Pas jin logon ne zulm kiya hai unke hissey ka bhi waisa hi azaab tayyar hai jaisa inhi jaise logon ko unke hissey ka mil chuka hai, iske liye yeh log jaldi na machayein"
  51,60,Aakhir ko tabahi hai kufr karne walon ke liye us roz jiska inhein khauff dilaya jaa raha hai